- SO I JUST DRINK BEER
AND CHASE TAIL.

24:12.140 --> 24:14.028
- [chuckles]
- IN BETWEEN MY DIAPER CHANGES.

24:14.070 --> 24:16.618
- [laughs]

24:16.660 --> 24:18.036
- WHAT'LL IT BE, HANDSOME?

24:18.070 --> 24:20.004
- WELL, YEAH,
I GOT TO HAVE THE B.L.T., YEAH.

24:20.040 --> 24:22.588
- THERE YOU GO.
- THANK YOU.

24:22.630 --> 24:24.837
- THERE'S MY MAN.

