AND SHE TELLS ME.

24:46.760 --> 24:47.749
[both chuckle]
- PERFECT.

24:47.790 --> 24:49.132
- YEAH.
- IT'S A GOOD PLAN.

24:49.170 --> 24:50.614
I KNOW THIS GUY.

24:50.660 --> 24:51.968
WHAT'S UP, MAN?
- THERE HE IS.

24:52.000 --> 24:53.729
- GOOD TO SEE YOU.
DAPPER.

24:53.760 --> 24:54.795
- HI.
- HI.

24:54.830 --> 24:55.694
- THAT'S MY FRIEND SARAH.
- SARAH.

24:55.730 --> 24:58.210
- WOMAN I WAS TCE)||__|LING YOU ABOUT.

