24:59.840 --> 25:02.217
- RIGHT. YEAH, CARL TOLD ME
THAT YOUR WORK IS AMAZING.

25:02.250 --> 25:04.115
- THANK YOU.
- OH, YEAH, AND I TOLD HIM

25:04.150 --> 25:05.287
THAT HE'D NEVER BE ABLE
TO AFFORD YOU.

25:05.330 --> 25:06.877
- [laughs]
- NOT TRUE, AT ALL.

25:06.910 --> 25:08.229
- A LITTLE BIT TRUE.

